  "title": "Hitting Reset on Life",
  "top_exclusions": [],
  "truncated_body_text": "When I kicked off this stage of my journey in 2020, I had a lot of ambition, very little experience, and just enough insight to be exactly wrong about 90% of things. But with drive, determination, and plenty of stupidity to keep me going, I learned everything I needed to know. And I did so without any of the success that I thought I needed along the way…",
